      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nouha Aouine" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nouha Aouine" href="/user/show/59336578-nouha-aouine">Nouha Aouine</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3978743460" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2013531997157319242">Reading Gibran in anything other than his original language does him a grave injustice, I realize. That did not, however, thwart the beauty of this work. The writing is mesmerizing with its dreamlike depictions, but the story itself is not as captivating as I had imagined it to be. Then again, perhaps romance is simply not my cup of tea. <br/><br/>I should reread this in Arabic to construct a more accurate vision. <br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


