              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5407952-jibran?shelf=arabic">arabic</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer877805582" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7470527099769905616">I read this in translation, in English and in Urdu, in fact, in three different Urdu translations, and I was struck by the lightning prose of Gibran. The dream-like, melancholic pining of the protagonist for his beautiful lover takes you to a realm of fantasy that is equally grounded in brutal reality of everyday life. It has been a long time I read it and now that I recall it after over a decade and a half, I am feeling nostalgic.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


