    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3939756486" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9624289060962377848">Beautiful and simultaneously depressing story. I want to reread this book as soon as possible again... and read other works of Kahlil Gibran. <br/>Even though I didn&apos;t understand the choises of Selma, I still liked the romance. And the ideas hidden in this book, rebellious and brave. All kinds of phrases that lets you think about the society and religion. <br/>I would recommend this book to anyone!</span>
  <span id="freeText9624289060962377848" style="display:none">Beautiful and simultaneously depressing story. I want to reread this book as soon as possible again... and read other works of Kahlil Gibran. <br />Even though I didn't understand the choises of Selma, I still liked the romance. And the ideas hidden in this book, rebellious and brave. All kinds of phrases that lets you think about the society and religion. <br />I would recommend this book to anyone!</span>
  <a data-text-id="9624289060962377848" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


