<div id="review_3869166289" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3869166289" />
    <a title="Nathalie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/130498241-nathalie"><img alt="Nathalie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1640905444p2/130498241.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3869166289?book_show_action=true">Apr 18, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nathalie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nathalie" href="/user/show/130498241-nathalie">Nathalie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3869166289" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17627959802217098616">I am an emotional mess. I have never encountered such a grave tragedy described in the most beautiful words of poetry with such care, detail, awareness, heartache, and bittersweet love and devotion. My heart weeps for Selma Karamy, and for all women who have suffered before her and since. I weep for all women with broken wings, unable to fly in the vast blue sky.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


